  MODULE .......: refufile
  TASK .........: Create a payment file from refund payments
  APPLICATION ..: tms
  AUTHOR .......: aam
  CREATED ......: 30.03.04
  CHANGED ......: 01.09.04/aam accept only Sampo
                  03.11.04/aam nordea has different end part in header
  Version ......: M15
